Suddenly, it shone brightly. What happened to my family...?
Hey, do you know?
Everything, adults are bad, right? Are you... an adult...?
Answer: Yes, I am an adult
Yeah, everything adults do is bad, right...?
W-Why am I in this situation...? You...please help me...?
W-Why am I in this situation...? C-Can you help me...?

Oh, let's go on a date and be happy together... How should
we do it? Ah, what should I do...?

\SE[9]This place... It feels strange... \SE[93]I... I'm a
little scared...

\SE[90]It's as if there's a hole in the very fabric of
space... \!\SE[91]I wonder what would happen if we were to
fall...

\SE[2]Um... Excuse me. \SE[0]Could you please tell me about
this place...?

Suddenly, a strong light flashed. What happened to my
family...? Hey, do you know?

\SE[74]To be honest... I don't think we can handle it....
\!\SE[75]It's not within our territory...\! What should we
do?

\SE[92]The Earth Spirit... \!\SE[93]I wonder if it's
somewhere in this place, lost...

\SE[76]If that's what you say, then we have no choice but to
continue exploring...
\SE[5]Ah, sorry... \!\SE[92]I didn't mean it that way...

\SE\SE[0]I-It's okay...! \SE[0]No matter what happens, I'll
protect you...! \SE[5]Probably...

\SE[69] (The atmosphere of the Trial of the Earth seems to
